
Juttele - The nice Android IRC client

Juttele is an IRC client for Android, with a focus on appearance and looking nice.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

This is the source code distribution of Juttele. If you are looking
for a compiled 'ready to use' version (APK), see the official
homepage at:

 http://max.sandholm.org/juttele

Juttele is not available at the Google Play Store yet, check back later.

If you are a developer and want to contribute to Juttele, checkout
our repository at GitHub:

 http://github.com/vurp0/Juttele

Juttele is a fork of the popular Android IRC client Yaaic:

 http://github.com/pocmo/Yaaic

--------------------------------------------------------------------

